data.description: $10,000 CREDIT (Buyer use towards Closing Costs/Painting/Flooring etc). Home features a covered front porch with an open layout upon entry, Large great Room with vaulted ceilings, Hardwood Floors throughout main living space, and a welcoming fireplace w/gas logs. Home also has several new light fixtures. Embrace yourself to an open dining room with an inviting kitchen [refrigerator to remain as gift] and granite counter tops. Eating area off kitchen overlooks private backyard. This home offers 3 Bedrooms on the main level, 2 Bathrooms, and Bonus Room over the garage. Master Bathroom features spacious walk-in closet, jetted tub, separate stand-up shower, and double sinks with granite counter tops. Large back yard that offers plenty of entertainment space for your next gathering to include concrete patio, deck with awning, and fire pit. Shed located to the rear of the home to remain for your necessary storage. This beautiful charm is just waiting for your finishing touches!
